512
00:44:35,924 --> 00:44:38,593
Ia adalah pilihannya.

513
00:44:40,261 --> 00:44:42,180
<i>Jangan lupa...</i>

514
00:44:42,263 --> 00:44:43,556
<i>Saya...</i>

515
00:44:44,391 --> 00:44:46,851
